        if chance of 50%:
            add (random integer between 1 and 3) of ink sac to player's inventory

        if chance of 40%:
            add (random integer between 1 and 4) of glass to player's inventory

        if chance of 30%:
            add 1 bookshelf to player's inventory

        if chance of 20%:
            add 1 lantern to player's inventory

        if chance of 10%:
            add 1 compass to player's inventory

        if chance of 5%:
            add 1 name tag to player's inventory

        send "&7Received Librarian loot."